B(x, \epsilon) = \{ y \in M \mid d(x,y) < \epsilon \}
\bar{B}(x, \epsilon) = \{ y \in M \mid d(x,y) \leqslant \epsilon \}
\bar{B}(x, \epsilon) = \overline{B(x, \epsilon)}
